Pest & Animal Control
A+ Rating With BBB Insured WSIB.Members OSPMA ,CPMA
Pesticon the name of knowledge and experience. Pest control with a professional approach. Pesticon Pest Control is engaged in providing the pest control for Mice, Termites, Bed bugs, Cockroaches, Millipedes, Centipedes, Silverfish, Wasps, Carpet Beetles, Fleas and all kinds of ants. We have the proven track record of over 80000 satisfied customers. By using the integrated Pest Management approach we give money back guarantee. We are licensed in Fumigation, Termites, Structural extermination. Experience the difference. Business with Ethics. Service beyond expectation.
service_area: Greater Toronto Area including Toronto,Pickering,Whitby,Ajax,Markham,Richmondhill,Thornhill,Vaughan,King City,Bolton,Brampton,Mississuaga,Oakville,Burlington,Georgetown and surrounding areas.

profile: Our pest removal services cover a range of pest that can be found in residential and commercial locations such as bugs, termites, raccoons, mice and more. Our team members are trained in the proper and humane removal of various pests and we ensure that will work to rid your location of harmful vermin. Many of the calls we attend are at locations that have a pest that is causing harm to the property or the health of the residents. You should never have to live with vermin, and we make sure we are available year round to keep your property pest free.
